  "body": "### Description\r\n\r\nThis is a rather important setting because:\r\n\r\n1. The default behavior changed in ORM 6, so application developers will surely need to set it when migrating.\r\n2. There is no \"one-size-fits-all\" solution, so depending on their DB and requirements, application developers may need to set it even when starting a new application.\r\n\r\nSee https://docs.jboss.org/hibernate/orm/current/userguide/html_single/Hibernate_User_Guide.html#_time_zone_storage\r\n\r\n### Implementation ideas\r\n\r\n_No response_",
